We are not the same, I am a Martian! 👽
-
DO NOT try being like the fitness model you see with a million followers. DO NOT drastically restrict your calories because you want to be as lean as someone else. DO NOT be selfish and arrogant because you're farther along than the person next to you! 👎🏼
-
I know how easy it is to get caught up in the "glamour" of fitness, that being shredded and having abs is the key to success. IT IS NOT. Fitness has shifted from being supportive and an enjoyable activity for most to being selfish and superficial. 😠
-
Fitness is for EVERYONE to participate in, no matter where you start. I believe that I have been given a chance to help change the culture of the fitness industry and I'll be DAMNED if I don't give it my best shot! 😏💪🏼
